"word":"present-day","count":1},{"word":"septimontian","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"respect","count":1},{"word":"admiration","count":1},{"word":"hope","count":1},{"word":"rise","count":1},{"word":"occasion","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"warrior","count":1},{"word":"crisis","count":1},{"word":"sure","count":1},{"word":"feel","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Phew. Hello, I'm Kastus. I fought these things from the outskirts all the way here. I'm spent, luckily you two were able to lend me a hand.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Yes, I understand. As you can see, the Dark Tide left many monstrosities in the Mournfell Canyon.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"But where there are challenges, there will always be Gladiators like me who'll come to hone our fighting skills.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"But I think I might have overestimated my abilities. Your form in combat showed me I have much room for improvement.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"I've watched your match with contender Lupa so many times that I've memorized every blow. But seeing you fight in person is a real eye-opener.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"An actual Champion is giving me training advice. Understood, I must start with the fundamentals!","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"Since you're both Gladiators, like me, I bet you're all amazed at the sights here.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"I only had to deal with the aftermath of the Dark Tide, and that left me exhausted. To think our heroes back then had to face it head-on while also ensuring the survival of Septimont.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"As a present-day Septimontian, I have nothing but respect and admiration for them.","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001},{"text":"I hope I can rise to the occasion as a true warrior in times of crisis. I'm sure you feel the same, don't you?","quest_name":"Uncovering Past Heroes","quest_id":936850001}]}